  <source>Stanford University</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To learn what effect, if any, Healing Touch (a gentle, non-invasive form of energy work that
      promotes relaxation and can help manage the side effects of chemotherapy and radiation), has
      on physical symptoms, mood, and qualify of life for women undergoing treatment for breast
      cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
